data.title: AWS Skills Center Seattle
data.meta_description: AWS Skills Center Seattle is a free training center for anyone in the Seattle community who is curious about cloud computing and future job possibilities in the cloud. The center is designed to help people with little to no technology background.
data.text:
Get Directions:

I-5 North:

Follow I-5 North to Olive Way exit, take EXIT 166

Turn slight RIGHT onto Olive Way

Turn LEFT onto Bellevue Ave

Take the 1st LEFT onto E Denny Way

Take the 2nd LEFT onto Stewart St

Turn RIGHT onto Terry Ave

Kumo will be on the LEFT

I-5 South:

Follow I-5 South to EXIT 166 towards Stewart St/Denny Way

Turn slight RIGHT onto Stewart St

Turn RIGHT onto Terry Ave

Kumo will be on the LEFT
